{"tid":666963,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★騰訊併購多　淨負債145億人幣 (2017年則為現金淨額163.32億元)","createTime":"2018-05-16T10:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T11:24:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fdae356b6dda12a00d887215942f9e71aa0ced9","tid":666963,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:32:14.000Z","msg":"騰訊控股(00700)業績披露，截至3月31日止，騰訊<span style=\"color: red;\">債務淨額145.33億元人民幣</span>(下同)，相比2017年12月31日則為現金淨額163.32億元。騰訊表示，雖然經營所得現金流量仍保持穩健，而本期轉為債務淨額狀態，主要由於併購項目的戰略投資增加，應付票據相應增加。於3月31日，騰訊於上市投資公司(不包括附屬公司)權益的公允價值合共2,126億元，而2017年12月31日為2,108億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://money18.on.cc/finnews/related_news_content.html?location=hk&amp;symbol=00700&amp;section=related_news&amp;article_id=bkn-20180516174632722-0516_00842_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmoney18.on.cc%2Ffinnews%2Frelated_news_content.html%3Flocation%3Dhk%26symbol%3D00700%26section%3Drelated_news%26article_id%3Dbkn-20180516174632722-0516_00842_001&d=YyqeJoGqwpmQPnUJQVY3cBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=635b294e\" target=\"_blank\">http://money18.on.cc/finnews/related_news_content.html?location=hk&amp;symbol=00700&amp;section=related_news&amp;article_id=bkn-20180516174632722-0516_00842_001</a>"},{"pid":"085da60f1d02b409f505c9f1e2db10b0a7e1bce7","tid":666963,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3f62dafdf3ba7b4ceb3b0a73e91b320b167c41","tid":666963,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:33:29.000Z","msg":"$250不是夢"},{"pid":"97e83137fa63f4f6b19e0cc8062e09b6da0f2c83","tid":666963,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20